Perform the following steps:

1. Click **Assign Networks**.

    ![Assign Networks pane in Ops Manager](images/azure/azs-networks-azure.png)

1. Under **Network**, select the PKS subnet you created for the PKS API VM. For example, `pks-network`.
1. Under **Service Network**, select the services subnet you created for Kubernetes cluster VMs. For example, `pks-services-network`.s
1. Click **Save**.
